				{
					"id": "443877",
					"author": {
						"name": "s.volkov",
						"key": "s.volkov",
						"displayName": "Sergey Volkov",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/Moscow"
					},
					"body": "I think this issue should be reopened, because it was not about general {{Promise}} support (native or polyfills).\r\nIt was about promise-based APIs vs callback-based, currently we still can not create native method which will return Promise to js side, all we have is old-school callback.\r\n\r\n-I have prepared POC for creating promise-based APIs for Android native modules:-\r\n* -[Branch|https://github.com/drauggres/titanium_mobile/commits/feature/promise-api]-\r\n* -[Builds|https://github.com/drauggres/titanium_mobile/releases/tag/v8.0.0.promise-preview]-\r\n\r\n-This is just {{proof-of-concept}} so I will not create PR from it (but feel free to use it if you'll find it worth).-\r\n\r\n-P.S. I don't think {{permissionRequest}} should reject Promise that was done only to show both resolving and rejection.-\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nI rethought everything above and cleaned up code: https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/pull/10554",
					"updateAuthor": {
						"name": "s.volkov",
						"key": "s.volkov",
						"displayName": "Sergey Volkov",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/Moscow"
					},
					"created": "2018-11-26T13:49:16.000+0000",
					"updated": "2018-12-20T12:30:40.000+0000"
				},
				{
